name: Reborn
description: Nachei created this image during his quarantine period in 2020. All the frustration generated during those times by not being able to leave home led to him finally creating his own landscapes to "escape" almost therapeutically. Reborn represents faith, a rebirth from darkness, a transition into a new era where we can rediscover the world around us.
